data.description: ** Rates stopping you from buying? Ask your agent/lender about negotiating a 2/1 buy down in the offer** Welcome to this gorgeous 5 bedroom, 4 full, 2 half bath home on over an acre in the highly desired Ruxton neighborhood, just outside of Towson, Md.  This house inside is timeless elegance and the private wooded setting will give you peace of mind and the perks of nature while being close to Baltimore and surrounding areas.  Located down a small side street and surrounded by nature this masterpiece sits at the end of a long circular driveway with a parking lot and two car garage at its end.  The entire main and upper levels are covered in quality wood flooring, the trim work and built ins throughout this home are both timeless and elegant.  The first floor has a gorgeous formal dining room, a massive living room area with fireplace, a family room with a fireplace, wet bar area, large center hall, powder room, and gourmet kitchen.  The kitchen has granite countertops and kitchen island, stainless appliances including double wall ovens.  Off of the kitchen is a large mudroom with ceramic tile and coat closets that leads out into the two car garage.  French doors from the main level open out onto a gorgeous bluestone courtyard style patio which is perfect for entertaining, outdoor dining and enjoying the surrounding forest. On the second floor are 4 bedrooms, one being the owners suite with vaulted ceilings, two custom walk in closets and a private bath with stand up shower, soaking tub and double vanities with marble finishes.  Another bedroom on this floor has its own private bath and fireplace, the remaining two bedrooms share a full bath in the upper hallway.  A door off of this level leads to a guest suite above the garage which hosts a 5th bedroom with vaulted ceilings, beautiful natural light and its own private full bath.  There is a second staircase that accesses this guest suite and the upper level from the main level. Heading down to the finished basement brings you to another finished living area, powder room, laundry facilities, and tons and tons of storage possibilities. This house has it all, and the details of this property both inside and out are sure to wow you!  Come see why it is the perfect home in the perfect location today!
